# Evaluation & Experimentation

## Metrics (Required)

Every experiment must measure and report:
- Precision@K, Recall@K
- MRR / nDCG
- Filter-specific: % wrong answers filtered, % correct answers retained

Store all results in `/evaluation/results/`.

## Experiment Rules

- NEVER mix experiment code with production pipeline
- Each experiment gets its own folder in `/experiments/`
- Each experiment includes: config file, logs, results
- Log: parameters used, filtering strategy, all metrics

```
/experiments/
  /semantic_filter_v1/
    config.yaml
    results.json
    analysis.ipynb
  /llm_filter_baseline/
    config.yaml
    results.json
```

## Testing

- Unit test all filters and scoring logic
- Test with known inputs/outputs
- Tests live in `/tests/` mirroring `/src/` structure
